Wafaa ki Tasveero!
Tumhen Watan ki Hawain 
Salam Kehti hain

Woh Sholay Apne Lahoo se Bhuja diye Tum ne
Bacha liya hai Yateemi se kitne Phoolon ko
Suhaag kitni Baharon ke Rakh liye Tumne
Tumhain Chaman ki Fazaain

Ali(Rza) Tumhari Shuja'at pe Jhoomtay hon ge

Tumhe Khuda ki Razaain Salam kehti hain

Shaheed ho ke kiya Maa'n ko Surkh roo Tum ne
Janab-e-Hazrat-e-Zainab(Rza) Gawahi deti hain

Watan ki Betiyan Maain Salam kehti hain
Aye Rah-e-Haq ke Shaheedo!
